{"tid":41182,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想幫屋企油油 想請教下大家","createTime":"2016-12-15T16:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T07:20:13.000Z","uid":6583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9c5e8fd10f5b17406f6be73311a4690ff5e047","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"由細到大油油都係交比老豆做。<br />\n呢幾年，老豆開始愈黎愈唔顧屋企，可以話係走左一半佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼見屋企D油又殘又舊，想屋企人住得開心D，所以想親力親為幫屋企油個靚油。但係我乜都唔識，想請教下大家⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我想問下，<br />\n我需要準備D咩？<br />\n要買咩材料？（最好有埋推介，中下價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n屋企人想要粉色（粉紅&amp;粉藍），呢兩隻色難唔難整？<br />\n同埋步驟係要點樣？<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位！萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55bc99439f8c4ac3beaca6f34df3efc5c1f57df","tid":41182,"uid":4626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"之前用開花生油定芥花子油？"},{"pid":"02a2cbfa962752ced278548b038feaadea91661d","tid":41182,"uid":61049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前用開花生油定芥花子油？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我建議用萬金油不含甲醛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f15ba0d496b792577b0e0a210336aaedd41a130","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前用開花生油定芥花子油？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心求解<br />\nBTW 芥花<span style=\"color: red;\">籽</span>"},{"pid":"1d4175d9f3c6e0eb17cc6e61e830d633705cb69d","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前用開花生油定芥花子油？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我建議用萬金油不含甲醛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屋企得返保心安油"},{"pid":"f24e57e2d86ea6cc29479d84b508977b63948dae","tid":41182,"uid":13029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"89256ef27c82d35f85289de211329cf7cef44833","tid":41182,"uid":23052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"買油<br />\n買大掃細掃<br />\n抹下啲牆<br />\n油天花 等乾 油多層<br />\n油牆 等乾 再乾 <br />\n大概係咁 <br />\n<br />\n利申 油過一次"},{"pid":"40f232592a8c5b9d074d4df3f69f5de426eeadab","tid":41182,"uid":41718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:31:26.000Z","msg":"用產場水，產灰，油底7，上灰再上灰再上灰，磨沙紙，油油，再油油，再油油，完"},{"pid":"9bf7bfd9e216111949f0ac9a6c8d2234c731fa29","tid":41182,"uid":15738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"可以影張牆身相睇睇牆身狀態嗎？"},{"pid":"056514299d3e09dbea0dd4daa4fbd02d6499b1ec","tid":41182,"uid":491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"舊既話冇得直接油，影張相上黎望下先"},{"pid":"fba8888133bd9393f0df8c6e3162d3d42b0dd71b","tid":41182,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"如果牆身靚,<br />\n但深色(紫)想轉淺色(米白)<br />\n係唔係一定要剷左舊油?<br />\n有無辨法直接油?"},{"pid":"6cd75461a8372d2018c21f1afefa0a9fe731d9a5","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以影張牆身相睇睇牆身狀態嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pR05RL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pR05RL.jpg&h=23a3ea7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/015525_495b3719112d2c72cafc51f8e9711613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F015525_495b3719112d2c72cafc51f8e9711613.jpg&h=3be7216c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z66q31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z66q31.jpg&h=3101a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊到痴線。。"},{"pid":"4c23af459e262ba4ccc3e8a5a3b2463594314953","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:56:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買油<br />\n買大掃細掃<br />\n抹下啲牆<br />\n油天花 等乾 油多層<br />\n油牆 等乾 再乾 <br />\n大概係咁 <br />\n<br />\n利申 油過一次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該你呀巴打 但係聽講牆太舊冇得就咁油 要剷走佢 跟住又唔知點"},{"pid":"99b327f3340082b5b89398e9f73e75a4b6bfd0e9","tid":41182,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"要批灰 好似係"},{"pid":"ab85e010570dbb2c636b5007139240dcb1f12bd5","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用產場水，產灰，油底7，上灰再上灰再上灰，磨沙紙，油油，再油油，再油油，完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係要買剷牆水、油、磨沙紙？<br />\n鏟灰係咪用下面果碌野？<br />\n<br />\n上灰係咩意思。。要買D咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0FE051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0FE051.jpg&h=61356610&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac2adfe42d13dc4908c5ff3838a99a59febc03be","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊既話冇得直接油，影張相上黎望下先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面有post 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d27998afe9fe4cd16526f1f6a90c2161cfb7aa","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要批灰 好似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係用牆鏟鏟走表面D野？<br />\nBtw使唔使飲住可樂鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d1135ddb79a5bc498b119f8cafee9fedf4bd2d","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:03:07.000Z","msg":"開post問漏左<br />\n牆窿要點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D窿真係好柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35WzKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35WzKLE.jpg&h=f3b0f2b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4627793c2b2a5a5a336069b10c1788cd8685b0cb","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果牆身靚,<br />\n但深色(紫)想轉淺色(米白)<br />\n係唔係一定要剷左舊油?<br />\n有無辨法直接油?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 可唔可以share你牆色比我參考下<br />\n順便再推一推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a163fbe6aed87bbfbfd589a7ed4f75551374bd","tid":41182,"uid":15738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"1）牆身幾大？<br />\n2）幾多幅牆要油？<br />\n3）住緊人同時油油？"},{"pid":"4ea3085bb6c4f9f47d908ce4beebaa06588266c0","tid":41182,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以影張牆身相睇睇牆身狀態嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pR05RL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pR05RL.jpg&h=23a3ea7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/015525_495b3719112d2c72cafc51f8e9711613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F015525_495b3719112d2c72cafc51f8e9711613.jpg&h=3be7216c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z66q31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z66q31.jpg&h=3101a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊到痴線。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你依d咁既狀態，好難就咁油油上去，因為你d灰都開始甩，可能要鏟底先上灰先油得靚同keep得耐..<br />\n<br />\n步驟係：<br />\n1.化白水溝水再噴牆等幾分鐘再鏟，不過依d睇你想點，出面大部分話鏟底翻油都係求其鏟幾下..<br />\n<br />\n2.跟住就油 水司拿..乾左再批灰，批好就散灰，用幼沙紙散滑牆身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.油底油，再油面油 起貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da169b9656baf87fa5a5a6e7b22a7b076c3dd1c8","tid":41182,"uid":15738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開post問漏左<br />\n牆窿要點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D窿真係好柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35WzKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35WzKLE.jpg&h=f3b0f2b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去五金舖買一罐石膏灰，再用你張相𠴱支摌「吻」平佢！"},{"pid":"8138ca5d737ce1a97388dac08481276fbe197ff4","tid":41182,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開post問漏左<br />\n牆窿要點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D窿真係好柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35WzKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35WzKLE.jpg&h=f3b0f2b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用石灰溝小小水，快速塞左去，因為石灰會收水，所以你批到幾平都好，乾左都會凹少少入去，最後批灰批順佢就ok"},{"pid":"6a62d1e2174e314325cf6259bbda1f7dba10d31f","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1）牆身幾大？<br />\n2）幾多幅牆要油？<br />\n3）住緊人同時油油？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1:Sorry呀我真係唔識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成間屋都要<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/021108_58f4d211541dc1c73abf666b903f4321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F021108_58f4d211541dc1c73abf666b903f4321.jpg&h=2ddc7874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平面圖大約係咁<br />\n<br />\n2.12幅<br />\n3.係呀。。得唔得架？呢D天氣好快乾到"},{"pid":"7f017f4277fb14dbf1eac73ce3dfc018a2322c59","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可以影張牆身相睇睇牆身狀態嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pR05RL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pR05RL.jpg&h=23a3ea7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/015525_495b3719112d2c72cafc51f8e9711613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F015525_495b3719112d2c72cafc51f8e9711613.jpg&h=3be7216c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z66q31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z66q31.jpg&h=3101a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊到痴線。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你依d咁既狀態，好難就咁油油上去，因為你d灰都開始甩，可能要鏟底先上灰先油得靚同keep得耐..<br />\n<br />\n步驟係：<br />\n1.化白水溝水再噴牆等幾分鐘再鏟，不過依d睇你想點，出面大部分話鏟底翻油都係求其鏟幾下..<br />\n<br />\n2.跟住就油 水司拿..乾左再批灰，批好就散灰，用幼沙紙散滑牆身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.油底油，再油面油 起貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該你呀好有心答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡！<br />\n不過我有少少地方唔明，散灰係咩意思？？<br />\n<br />\n我要買既材料<br />\n1.化白水<br />\n2.水司拿<br />\n3.幼沙紙（上面巴打話磨沙紙 係咪一樣野黎？）<br />\n4.油<br />\n<br />\n有冇漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74313bdacfd00f7b54097e483971d798fc5688a2","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開post問漏左<br />\n牆窿要點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D窿真係好柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35WzKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35WzKLE.jpg&h=f3b0f2b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去五金舖買一罐石膏灰，再用你張相𠴱支摌「吻」平佢！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有仲有。。有D膠嘴係個窿入面<br />\n可以點拎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8d01fd96322664ab50072cabd257aa4eb4482c","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開post問漏左<br />\n牆窿要點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D窿真係好柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35WzKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35WzKLE.jpg&h=f3b0f2b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用石灰溝小小水，快速塞左去，因為石灰會收水，所以你批到幾平都好，乾左都會凹少少入去，最後批灰批順佢就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n批灰係咩 灰=石灰？ 用支鏟整d石灰落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde44809e8be862bcf29d3ac8934cde45f85cad8","tid":41182,"uid":59696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"巴打，批灰唔係講就做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你諗住全屋剷灰，你又住緊人，又有傢俬，都幾麻煩"},{"pid":"1d3839c55ca0b939c4f781bfe2b53d64b27e2c70","tid":41182,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開post問漏左<br />\n牆窿要點補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D窿真係好柒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35WzKLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35WzKLE.jpg&h=f3b0f2b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用石灰溝小小水，快速塞左去，因為石灰會收水，所以你批到幾平都好，乾左都會凹少少入去，最後批灰批順佢就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n批灰係咩 灰=石灰？ 用支鏟整d石灰落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講錯，石膏先岩"},{"pid":"77c6b178b58324d3092ecd8f213381645024bd1f","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/022348_c322080ac399ff4e0071bab53e707d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F022348_c322080ac399ff4e0071bab53e707d72.jpg&h=bdb0b3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅牆係咪可以就咁油？"},{"pid":"5e31e29dee527ebd3765478a074bbe8044053892","tid":41182,"uid":13029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:24:56.000Z","msg":"批灰 係咪要自己溝 定係有得買？"},{"pid":"0c8ccd774d424230271777faa578d2ac64b8df26","tid":41182,"uid":5232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:26:04.000Z","msg":"一定要用紫花油，再加油漆，開岀黎先有果陣香味，又有少少紫色"},{"pid":"e269fda5eb8f082aff095b84d661b456241fff8a","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，批灰唔係講就做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你諗住全屋剷灰，你又住緊人，又有傢俬，都幾麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企傢私唔多 要搬好容易搬到架<br />\n<br />\n如果分開幾日做會唔會好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b52fac278a1df420c4d4cebe946d85a270841d","tid":41182,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:26:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果牆身靚,<br />\n但深色(紫)想轉淺色(米白)<br />\n係唔係一定要剷左舊油?<br />\n有無辨法直接油?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 可唔可以share你牆色比我參考下<br />\n順便再推一推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n類似呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20090110/large/10bb6615pa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20090110%2Flarge%2F10bb6615pa.jpg&h=13a63715&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2b82a0f712da2e4dd616cf6b48bce3a00551c1d","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>批灰 係咪要自己溝 定係有得買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q8-e2gQgEK8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%