\n<br />\n剷灰＞批灰＞磨灰<br />\n已經將屋企變咗地盤咁<br />\n仲要同時住緊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住朝早整到晚 叫佢地出去玩夜晚先返"},{"pid":"e7befc6fba89580568e519a4381c31716a4b5488","tid":41182,"uid":6946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，批灰唔係講就做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你諗住全屋剷灰，你又住緊人，又有傢俬，都幾麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剷灰＞批灰＞磨灰<br />\n已經將屋企變咗地盤咁<br />\n仲要同時住緊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住朝早整到晚 叫佢地出去玩夜晚先返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n掃都掃撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc43720e142f9f694ab252278a33a1d7e3673671","tid":41182,"uid":15738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/032427_2831600fef7c337d71e69943fc70a8e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F032427_2831600fef7c337d71e69943fc70a8e7.jpg&h=ce404189&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/032428_6be749dc44d2626b60b55e005463ae99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F032428_6be749dc44d2626b60b55e005463ae99.jpg&h=ecf61898&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEYZvd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEYZvd5.jpg&h=6c5b0b01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/032429_b73d520593a3b9d15e4ecc1a2639017f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F032429_b73d520593a3b9d15e4ecc1a2639017f.jpg&h=f883d300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我淨係剷條坑藏條光纖去右邊個櫃、批灰再磨灰已經成間屋都係灰粉，老婆抹足成星期，當然亦哦足成星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩「痴」完牆紙效果幾好先冇哦落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63eebe9b985d865b6231110cc9d606a71dd67af","tid":41182,"uid":15738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T19:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打，批灰唔係講就做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你諗住全屋剷灰，你又住緊人，又有傢俬，都幾麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企傢私唔多 要搬好容易搬到架<br />\n<br />\n如果分開幾日做會唔會好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你間屋成400呎，搵專業做都要成個星期啦起碼！"},{"pid":"c49ceb93be933720fc4dd73ead73fd2898283f3b","tid":41182,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企傢私唔多 要搬好容易搬到架<br />\n<br />\n如果分開幾日做會唔會好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你點都要分幾日做，加上你唔熟手做，批灰好難批得快同順，批灰你要識放灰同收灰...唔係淨係刮下刮下咁，同埋最緊要唔好批到d灰一舊舊..多數新手都會有依d問題，你要keep住個批池乾淨..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪批到平滑就OK?<br />\n呀係。。要買D咩架生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買個 灰板 批池（金星鏝個隻，比較軟身..幾多寸就自己中意） 4寸漆鏟 （鏟灰用！你有d灰好難鏟就唔好鏟，鏟好晒就甩既灰就油司拿） 油掃（最少2把）沙紙 （我唔記得幾多度沙紙了，有d沙紙磚，一舊海錦黎，比沙紙包住，同五金鋪講散灰用就得！）"},{"pid":"30164ecd7afb69e8873dd43fe517a73ea9f181e1","tid":41182,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有現成  但計落會貴d<br />\n但自己唔識開就唔好計呢d喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我買現成好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔想搞咁多野 溝錯左仲衰<br />\n係咪就咁係五金鋪講話買批灰<span style=\"color: red;\">果D灰</span>就可以買到？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得菜膠福粉好批d..現成灰比較硬身，如果手勢唔好，散灰好辛苦，不過你注意唔好漏d灰屎（姐係成粒痴左係牆到）係牆到問題不大"},{"pid":"c97cf74f11ae42967e14c76c24531c1dca3f0f3a","tid":41182,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:13:41.000Z","msg":"巴打 你搞油油 最好成家搬開曬d野黎搞 <br />\n一黎就住就住 油到一達達<br />\n二黎搞到成屋灰塵 清潔又難"},{"pid":"c3e287f7ea935f3f40ed4d95edd23c1db4fa11b7","tid":41182,"uid":6583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/032427_2831600fef7c337d71e69943fc70a8e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F032427_2831600fef7c337d71e69943fc70a8e7.jpg&h=ce404189&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/032428_6be749dc44d2626b60b55e005463ae99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F032428_6be749dc44d2626b60b55e005463ae99.jpg&h=ecf61898&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEYZvd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEYZvd5.jpg&h=6c5b0b01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/032429_b73d520593a3b9d15e4ecc1a2639017f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F032429_b73d520593a3b9d15e4ecc1a2639017f.jpg&h=f883d300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我淨係剷條坑藏條光纖去右邊個櫃、批灰再磨灰已經成間屋都係灰粉，老婆抹足成星期，當然亦哦足成星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩「痴」完牆紙效果幾好先冇哦落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n間屋大家都有一齊住 同埋都同意我做<br />\n相信我屋企人唔會怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係正係驚唔識整"},{"pid":"9c289b1a992d29474178a5d80f48f71f911d0747","tid":41182,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:45:35.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆  就算你買齊料<br />\n都係去youtube睇下人地個步驟係點做先<br />\n填窿可以用隻叫填縫膠既配玻璃槍"}]}